{"analytics_identifier":"OT1348","base_path":"/government/organisations/evaluation-task-force","content_id":"0560f300-8c13-4da1-b1a2-664d13d635bb","description":"We are a joint Cabinet Office-HM Treasury unit providing specialist support to ensure evidence and evaluation sits at the heart of spending decisions. ETF works with the Cabinet Office and HM Treasury .","details":{"acronym":"ETF","alternative_format_contact_email":"etf@cabinetoffice.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We are a joint Cabinet Office-HM Treasury unit providing specialist support to ensure evidence and evaluation sits at the heart of spending decisions.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Evaluation Task Force\">ETF</abbr> works with the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/cabinet-office\">Cabinet Office</a> and <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/hm-treasury\">HM Treasury</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"cabinet-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Evaluation Task Force"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/major-shift-in-government-evaluation-as-magenta-book-is-updated","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a06db10ee62840dba48a306/s712_Untitled.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a06db1097000cb6073e4e67/s465_Untitled.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a06db1097000cb6073e4e68/Untitled.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-05-15T09:36:16.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Evaluation Task Force has released the 2026 update to the Magenta Book, the government’s central guidance on evaluation. As the most significant revision in government evaluation standards since 2020, it marks a major milestone for evidence-based policymaking.</p>\n</div>","title":"Major shift in government evaluation as Magenta Book is updated"},{"document_type":"Corporate report","href":"/government/publications/evaluation-academy-final-evaluation-report","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69023baf918e1f940b3cf82b/s712_Image_1.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69023baf3650bacb01af7087/s465_Image_1.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69023baf6d9e8bf43eaf70ad/Image_1.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-10-29T15:46:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Evaluation Task Force has published their evaluation of the July 2025 Evaluation Academy training programme.</p>\n</div>","title":"Evaluation Academy - Final Evaluation Report"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/the-evaluation-registry-a-new-home-for-government-evaluation","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68762430cfc3756455bb6a12/s712_Evaluation_Registry__1_.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68762430a8d0255f9fe28e8b/s465_Evaluation_Registry__1_.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6876243088da2e5804bb6a20/Evaluation_Registry__1_.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-07-11T09:09:53.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>In March this year, the Evaluation Task Force launched the Evaluation Registry: a website which will act as a single home for evaluations across Government. </p>\n</div>","title":"The Evaluation Registry: a new home for Government evaluation"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/new-guidance-for-evaluating-the-impact-of-ai-tools","image":{"alt_text":"Graphic illustration showing a person working at a desktop computer","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67975f73e0edc3fbb06062e3/s712_AI_Guidance_News_Article_Image.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67975f73fe1eabe7d7a22c5b/s465_AI_Guidance_News_Article_Image.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67975f73cbd1e3a508a22c5c/AI_Guidance_News_Article_Image.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-01-27T00:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Evaluation Task Force have recently published a new annex to the Magenta Book which covers best practice for impact evaluation of AI tools and technologies.</p>\n</div>","title":"New Guidance for Evaluating the Impact of AI Tools"}],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":true,"organisation_type":"other","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[{"href":"https://twitter.com/WhatWorksUK","service_type":"twitter","title":"What Works"},{"href":"https://whatworks.blog.gov.uk/","service_type":"blog","title":"What Works Blog"}]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2021-12-10T13:00:52+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1348","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/evaluation-task-force","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/evaluation-task-force","base_path":"/government/organisations/evaluation-task-force","content_id":"0560f300-8c13-4da1-b1a2-664d13d635bb","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-08-27T09:17:05Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Evaluation Task Force","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/evaluation-task-force","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_contacts":[{"content_id":"538a378a-48db-4ef1-b2b7-33e60ed09501","details":{"contact_form_links":null,"description":"Including enquiries about the What Works Network and the Evaluation Academy","email_addresses":[{"email":"etf@cabinetoffice.gov.uk"}],"phone_numbers":null,"post_addresses":[],"title":"Evaluation Task Force